# Playwright MCP â€” Project Configuration
# ========================================
#
# Format: project_name | google_account | directories (space-separated, supports *)
#
# - project_name:    any name you want (no spaces)
# - google_account:  your Google email, or "clean" for no account
# - directories:     where you run Claude Code from (supports * globs)
#
# First project listed becomes the default.
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Example:

work       | you@company.com   | ~/projects/company-*
personal   | you@gmail.com     | ~/
side-gig   | you@sidegig.com   | ~/projects/sidegig-*
dev        | clean             | ~/projects/experiments ~/projects/oss-*
